rComments: Either you get RSM222 or you don't. Gus is the best prof out of the many, he is helpful and understanding. Just do the problems, and learn to do them super fast. The test is based not on whether you know how to do things, but how fast you are at doing them. With that said, not a hard course at all if you spend time to do the homework. RSM222RSM220
